stableaudio3-ios

This repository contains Swift and Python code for running converted Stable
Audio 3 Small Music and Small SFX weights on iOS with MLX Swift.

No Stability AI or Google model weights are included in this repository.

When used with Stable Audio 3 weights, the model is licensed under the
Stability AI Community License:

