Stable Audio 3 uses T5Gemma for text conditioning. Gemma is provided under and
subject to the Gemma Terms of Use found at ai.google.dev/gemma/terms.

Users are responsible for accepting and complying with the upstream model
licenses and use policies before downloading, converting, distributing, or using
model weights.
